## Technologies Covered

- **PNM (Phyllotactic Neural Meshing / Phyllux Mesh)** - Neural electrode array concepts
- **GAFAA (Golden-Angle Fractal Antenna Arrays / Phyllux Wave)** - Antenna array concepts
- **Phyllux Vault** (formerly PhiKey) - Geometric cryptographic concepts
- **Integrated Biomimetic System (IBS / PhiNexus)** - System integration concepts

